// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1625 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 0455126b-d8c4-5780-bb74-386428d11644

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
